                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "0 ~ ^ { \\circ } \\mathbf C"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": " and stirred for 5 minutes. To the reaction mixture R-9 (50 mg, 0.24l mmol) is added and the reaction mixture is stirred for 1O minutes. The reaction mixture is concentrated in vacuo. The crude product is purified by preparative HPLC to afford Example 71 (22 mg, 35%)."
                    }
